> ----------
> From: 	Harshbarger, Robert[SMTP:bharsh@puget.com]
> Sent: 	Friday, October 05, 2001 9:17 AM
> To: 	Interchange Scheduling & Accounting Subcommittee (ISAS)
> Subject: 	FW: WSCC Tagging practices
